== 对岸天使 ==
[[Image:Vilnius_Uzupio_Respublica.jpg|thumb]]
2002年4月1日，一個吹小號的天使雕像在廣場上揭幕，象徵該區藝術自由的復興。這個想法是從建立一個天使雕像以紀念動畫師和漫畫家澤諾納斯·史泰尼斯（{{lang|lt|Zenonas Šteinys}}）的願望而發展起來的。<ref>{{Cite web|title=H E R I T A G E Lithuanian Footsteps on the World's Cinema A Grand Undertaking: The Radvila Map of Lithuania They Tore Down Le|url=http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:IXAoQIApD48J:www.draugas.org/key_dnlh/lh/issues/2007-05-15-LHERITAGE.pdf+&cd=5&hl=en&ct=clnk&gl=uk|access-date=2021-02-22|website=webcache.googleusercontent.com|archive-date=2021-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724084454/http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache%3AIXAoQIApD48J%3Awww.draugas.org%2Fkey_dnlh%2Flh%2Fissues%2F2007-05-15-LHERITAGE.pdf+&cd=5&hl=en&ct=clnk&gl=uk|dead-url=no}}</ref>這個雕像成了對岸共和國復興的象徵。建立資金通過出售雕像的微型複製品籌集的。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://kauno.diena.lt/naujienos/vilniaus-miestas/simbolis-uzupio-angelas-iskilo-mazu-kopiju-240395|title=Simbolis: Užupio angelas iškilo iš mažų kopijų|access-date=2021-07-24|archive-date=2021-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724084500/https://kauno.diena.lt/naujienos/vilniaus-miestas/simbolis-uzupio-angelas-iskilo-mazu-kopiju-240395|dead-url=no}}</ref>雕塑家羅馬斯·維爾恰斯卡斯（{{lang|lt|Romas Vilčiauskas}}）作為对岸天使的創造者，亦創作了「對岸美人魚」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fotobankas.lt/fotografija/list/search/Romo+Vil%C4%8Diausko+undin%C4%97l%C4%97 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2012-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151226140814/http://www.fotobankas.lt/fotografija/list/search/Romo+Vil%C4%8Diausko+undin%C4%97l%C4%97 |archive-date=2015-12-26 |url-status=yes }}</ref>

在此之前，同樣的位置是一個雞蛋的臨時雕塑。被較大的对岸天使雕像取代後，雞蛋以10200[[立特|立特]]被拍賣出售，現矗立在Pylimo街上。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Margutis Easter Egg|url=http://www.atlasobscura.com/places/margutis-easter-egg|access-date=2021-07-27|work=Atlas Obscura|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210727043204/https://www.atlasobscura.com/places/margutis-easter-egg|dead-url=no}}</ref>
